{"tid":1441211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[談判籌碼] 暫停一周上街，換取主要訴求，否則下個weekend繼續","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:44:53.000Z","uid":284284,"like":52,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"377f993cc0b306e99c93dcf1d9629ac58ddd8c5a","tid":1441211,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"如果上街係我哋嘅最大籌碼，咁係咪應該好好利用？<br />\n港共615之後冇再讓過一步，而我哋亦都已經連續10個weekend &quot;無條件&quot; 地上街<br />\n即係話 &quot;一個平靜嘅weekend&quot; 已經成為咗我哋手上嘅談判籌碼<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該試下提出 <br />\n&quot;暫停一周上街，回復香港平靜，畀足時間空間政府，換取主要訴求，否則下個weekend繼續&quot;<br />\n即係例如<br />\n我哋8月17,18號唔上街，踢返個波畀政府，換取政府讓步, 回應主要訴求<br />\n如果唔回應，下個weekend 24,25號繼續上街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c698aa6abb8e7d080b3397e9d9637883640a18a","tid":1441211,"uid":73717,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"認同 set deadline 一個星期 <br />\n比人知如果政府願意正面回應 做到五大訴求<br />\n抗爭者係絕對可以 隨時 會停止活動"},{"pid":"a5794fb3ca93a4e3255f9dcaf2ccb15760501453","tid":1441211,"uid":284284,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"如果同意嘅唔該幫推"},{"pid":"d0ef0b898c05e8f745a23f1f73777c6661f887e0","tid":1441211,"uid":131646,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"諗得過 手足又可以抖下強身健體"},{"pid":"e24f4a82608f365a8ce7a1ebe0714c7e8bbdc09d","tid":1441211,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47ab285dee92d25cbcaad58218a1b62da32bc67b","tid":1441211,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n但係真係小心大搜捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif